TensorCash Modifications
================================================================================

  Copyright (c) 2024-2025 The TensorCash Core developers

TensorCash Core extends Bitcoin Core with the following functionality:

  - TensorCash chain type (tensor, tensor-test, tensor-reg) with dedicated
    network parameters, genesis block, and consensus rules
  - Cross-chain atomic swap contract system (forward, spot, repo contracts)
  - Confidential compute bridge sessions with SAS verification
  - Zero-knowledge proof infrastructure (ZK params manager, commitment proofs)
  - Governance and treasury subsystem
  - Asset balance tracking and price feeds
  - Mining API integration for decentralised compute marketplace
  - AI model marketplace interface
  - P2P exchange with cross-chain trade view
  - Post-quantum cryptography (liboqs / secp256k1-zkp integration)
  - Tor-integrated privacy networking (TorManager)
  - TensorCash-branded QT desktop interface

All TensorCash modifications are distributed under the same MIT License as the
original Bitcoin Core software. See the COPYING file for the full license text.

